    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a dependable daily driver for someone who isn't concerned with minor cosmetic imperfections. The engine and transmission are functional, though you may notice some typical age-related wear and occasional minor leaks that are common for its mileage. The exterior shows some noticeable scratches, small door dings, and some fading on the clear coat, while the interior has visible wear on the upholstery and a few cracked plastic trim pieces. It has been maintained reasonably well, but it will likely require some minor repairs or part replacements in the near future to keep it running optimally.",
