      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly project or a fixer-upper with potential? This vehicle has plenty of stories to tell and definitely shows its age, featuring significant wear and tear that reflects its journey. While it will require some dedicated mechanical attention and cosmetic TLC to get it back into shape, it's an affordable entry point for a DIY enthusiast ready to roll up their sleeves!",
