      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride and it's looking for a new home. It\u2019s been so reliable and still runs like a dream! The interior is super clean, and it\u2019s clearly been well-loved over the years. Perfect for someone who wants a solid, comfortable car without the brand-new price tag. Come take it for a spin\u2014I know you\u2019ll love it as much as I do!",
