    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 inline-six with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. This example retains its crisp 8,000 RPM redline and delivers linear power through a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-variable differential lock. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement, ensuring structural rigidity under high lateral loads. The suspension geometry remains tight, and the induction note is quintessential BMW M. A mechanically sound enthusiast's spec ready for spirited canyon carving.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
