    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained 2017 Audi S5 Prestige in Navarra Blue Metallic over a Rotor Gray leather interior. This car has been my pride and joy, and it shows in the mechanical upkeep. The exterior paint retains a deep, glass-like shine, though there are a few minor stone chips on the front hood and a small 1-inch scuff on the lower rear bumper, consistent with careful daily use. Inside, the cabin is smoke-free and features Carbon Atlas inlays; the leather bolsters show only light natural creasing with no tears or stains. All electronics, including the Virtual Cockpit and Bang & Olufsen sound system, function perfectly. Mechanically, the car is stout. It has a full-service history from authorized dealers, with the most recent oil service and spark plug replacement completed just 1,500 miles ago. The Michelin Pilot Sport 4S tires have approximately 70% tread remaining. This is a solid, honest example of a modern performance coupe that is ready for its next owner.",
